  You may not impose any further restrictions on the exercise of the
rights granted or affirmed under Copyleft-Next.

  Further restrictions include alleging in litigation that a patent
claim is infringed by making, using, selling, offering for sale, or
importing the Received Work or any portion of it.

  Distribution of a Covered Work incorporating material covered by the
following free software licenses is not imposition of a "further
